<br />I've already make some mods with 2 x 27c160 (much easier than this one ^^), but this time I don't know how to proceed..
<br />
<br />Eproms seems to be soldered/connected correctly as its not my first time and I've verified every connections few times (just in case). 
<br />
<br />I've already make a thing on the board : lift MAD-1 pin 13 and connect it to A22 (which is connected to pin 48 )
<br />
<br />How to connect eproms correctly with the mad-1, with a 74ls139 or a 74ls138 I suppose ?, maybe not...
